  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-6 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This clean package demonstrates a complete 13-factor assessment at Model Risk Level 5 where a subset of factors are marked not-applicable with fully documented rationale. All assessed factors meet or exceed required credibility levels. Factors scoped out of the ASME V&V 40 framework (e.g., those originating from NASA-specific guidance or aerospace verification traditions) carry explicit documented justification explaining why they fall outside the scope of this Class III cardiovascular device submission. Decision: Accepted.",
